 TEIform=\"title\">Abst.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.26</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἱ πόνοι ὄ. τοῖς ἀγαθοῖς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg007.perseus-grc1:7:5:80\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cyr.\">Cyr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.5.80</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n76358.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> at Athens, esp.<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fish</tr_>, the chief delicacy of the Athenians (<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πολλῶν ὄντων ὄ. ἐκνενίκηκεν ὁ ἰχθὺς μόνος ἢ μάλιστά γε ὄψον καλεῖσθαι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.667f</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:276e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.276e</biblScope> </bibl>); so in Pap., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄ</foreign>. as collective, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fish, PCair. Zen.</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:82:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">82.17</biblScope> </bibl> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B. C.)</date>; in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg036:1:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mul.\">Mul.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.37</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὄψα θαλάσσια</foreign> is <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.l.</abbr> (dub.). </sen